snippet.title: 100 Rogues - "How to Play"
snippet.description:
This is the 100 Rogues (for iPhone & iPod Touch) "How to Play" video which attempts to explain the mechanics of 100 Rogues to you foolish adventurers. 100 Rogues is coming out very, very soon!  Visit our site!

www.100rogues.com

Music & Editing by Keith Burgun
100 Rogues is created by Dinofarm Games & Fusion Reactions.
